From 9342012e3f567266a0df46bf20cec83729068ad4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Jensen, Pete" <jensenp@hmc.harvard.edu>
Date: Tue, 21 Apr 2026 16:44:55 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 6/7] test(indexing): migrate to xunit.v3, drop
 Xunit.Microsoft.DependencyInjection
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

xunit.runner.visualstudio 3.x requires xunit.v3 — mixing it with
xunit 2.x broke live ITestOutputHelper output in VS 2026.

Replace TestBed<T>/TestBedFixture pattern with native xunit.v3
IClassFixture<T> + IAsyncLifetime. Fixtures now own their own
IServiceProvider built directly via ServiceCollection.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
